snippet.title: Amber Portwood SECRET AUDIO LEAKED: SHOCKING AUDIO & ARREST DETAILS
snippet.description:
Amber Portwood was arrested on July 5th, 2019 for domestic violence.  But in a strange and shocking twist of events, it was what came AFTER the arrest that shocked the world.  Secret Audio files released, details emerge of what is happening now with Court.
